relevant_findings.HEENT: Atraumatic/normocephalic, extraocular movements intact, pupils equal, round, reactive to light, anicteric sclera, pink conjunctiva, patent nares, moist mucous membranes, good dentition
relevant_findings.neck: Nontender, supple, no lymphadenopathy, no jugular venous distention
relevant_findings.cardiac: Regular rate and rhythm, S1/S2, no murmurs, gallops, or rubs
relevant_findings.lung: Clear to auscultation bilaterally, no wheezes, rales, rhonchi, breathing comfortably without use of accessory muscles
relevant_findings.abdomen: Nondistended, positive bowel sounds, tender in lower abdomen without rebound
relevant_findings.extremities: Trace edema in left leg, chronic
relevant_findings.neurological: Cranial nerves II-XII intact, moving all extremities with purpose, excellent historian
